sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSP Driver)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: ML Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE type schema<br/>MySQL/PG wire protocol, Optional SSL
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (type_id)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionTypeResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution<br/>(execution + artifacts + events + contexts)
    Note right of MLMD: Atomic operation:<br/>new DB connection per RPC<br/>optimistic concurrency control
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT execution, artifacts, events
    DB-->>MLMD: OK (entity IDs)
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse<br/>(execution_id, artifact_ids)

    DSP->>MLMD: PutAttributionsAndAssociations<br/>(context ↔ artifact/execution links)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT attribution/association rows
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutAttributionsAndAssociationsResponse

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    participant Client as Pipeline UI / Client

    Client->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    Note right of MLMD: Graph traversal with<br/>configurable depth,<br/>direction, ending conditions
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with ZetaSQL-parsed filters<br/>recursive graph traversal queries
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (nodes + edges)
    MLMD-->>Client: GetLineageSubgraphResponse<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)

    Client->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>(list artifacts in pipeline context)
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts<br/>JOIN attributions WHERE context_id=?
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact rows
    MLMD-->>Client: GetArtifactsByContextResponse<br/>(paginated artifacts list)
